description.narrative: A large part of Muhammadiyah University Aceh (Unmuha) campus was destroyed during the 2004 Boxing Day earthquake/tsunami, hampering faculty and students's teaching and learning activities. The Activity will construct and fit out a new classroom block and library/laboratory building to restore and provide a better learning environment for Unmuha's 4,000 students and 360 staff.
